(:summary    "Simple task timer package"
 :license    "GPL-2"
 :authors    (("Jeremy Cowgar" . "jeremy@cowgar.com"))
 :maintainer ("Jeremy Cowgar" . "jeremy@cowgar.com")
 :provided   (task-timer)
 :keywords   ("task-timer" "timer")
 :homepage   "http://www.emacswiki.org/TaskTimer"
 :wikipage   "http://www.emacswiki.org/TaskTimer"
 :commentary "\
This package allows you to time an activity. Start the timer then
when stoppig the timer it will report the amount of time elapsed

Requirements:

Only tested on Emacs 23

Installation:

Add below code in your .emacs

(require 'task-timer)")
